sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant KonfluxCI as Konflux CI
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>registry.redhat.io<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as rhods-operator<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard
    participant User as User Browser
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>(Envoy)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant JupyterLab as JupyterLab<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant CodeSrv as code-server<br/>80/TCP HTTP
    participant Culler as Notebook Culler
    participant Elyra as Elyra Plugin
    participant DSPA as DSPA Endpoint<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/S
    participant Runtime as Runtime Image<br/>(batch pod)
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over KonfluxCI,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Image Build and Deployment
        KonfluxCI->>Registry: Push built images<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Service account token
        Operator->>Operator: Read params.env /<br/>params-latest.env
        Operator->>K8sAPI: Apply ImageStream manifests<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Service account
        K8sAPI->>Registry: Pull images (on pod schedule)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Pull secret
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over User,JupyterLab: Flow 2: Workbench User Session (Jupyter)
        User->>Gateway: HTTPS request<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.3<br/>OAuth/OIDC
        Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward to sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Bearer Token
        KRBAC->>JupyterLab: Proxy to JupyterLab<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>Pod-internal (no auth)
        JupyterLab-->>KRBAC: Response
        KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>User: HTML/JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Culler,CodeSrv: Flow 3: Idle Culling
        Culler->>KRBAC: Poll idle status<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS<br/>Service account token
        KRBAC->>JupyterLab: GET /api/kernels/<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>Pod-internal
        JupyterLab-->>KRBAC: Kernel status JSON
        KRBAC-->>Culler: Idle/active status

        Note over Culler,CodeSrv: (code-server variant)
        Culler->>KRBAC: Poll idle status<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS
        KRBAC->>CodeSrv: GET /api/kernels/<br/>80/TCP HTTP → httpd CGI 8080/TCP
        CodeSrv-->>KRBAC: Fake kernel status<br/>(access.cgi polls /codeserver/healthz)
        KRBAC-->>Culler: Idle/active status
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 230)
        Note over Elyra,S3: Flow 4: Elyra Pipeline Execution
        Elyra->>DSPA: Submit pipeline<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS<br/>Bearer Token
        DSPA->>Runtime: Launch batch pod<br/>Service account
        Runtime->>S3: Download notebook/data<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM
        S3-->>Runtime: Artifacts
        Runtime-->>DSPA: Execution complete
    end
